{"tid":1453542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日蘋果A12版 8月12日","createTime":"2019-08-12T04:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T04:37:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"847da2c07c39172b96868bdaa3bc28bd71cbd50f","tid":1453542,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:33:34.000Z","msg":"今日蘋果A12版 8月12日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o1URenF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo1URenF.jpg&h=9d8fac3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tJhzb9m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtJhzb9m.jpg&h=0f127824&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"262518e58633d8b9dfcaca0181a57f5442777bf1","tid":1453542,"uid":122601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:35:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44d25f420aecf05c6a9caf0940fa7be79c255de1","tid":1453542,"uid":103102,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:37:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港需要人道救援</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當下，香港極需要不受滋擾的中立醫療團隊。我們需要無國界醫生、聯合國維和部隊，以及其他人道救援組織。只有他們可以為香港提供正常醫療保障，免於中共香港警察滋擾。以下這個聯署，是要求美國派遣醫療船以提供中立的醫療服務。美國醫療船扺達後，其他國際醫療組織就更易來港協助，以減低香港人在今次戰爭的傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n這是十分實際的要求，也是極為急切和重要。為免香港發生大規模人道災難，請各位簽署並廣傳！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-medical-army-hong-kong-hong-kong-under-humanitarian-disaster\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-send-medical-army-hong-kong-hong-kong-under-humanitarian-disaster&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpDC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=38438220\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-medical-army-hong-kong-hong-kong-under-humanitarian-disaster</a>"}]}